- [ConfigForgeApp.swift](mdc:ConfigForgeApp.swift) - Main entry point
- [ConfigForge/](mdc:ConfigForge) - Main application code
  - [Models/](mdc:ConfigForge/Models) - Data models for SSH and Kubernetes configs
  - [Views/](mdc:ConfigForge/Views) - SwiftUI views for the application
  - [ViewModels/](mdc:ConfigForge/ViewModels) - Business logic for views
  - [Services/](mdc:ConfigForge/Services) - Services for file management and parsing
  - [Utilities/](mdc:ConfigForge/Utilities) - Helper functions and utilities
  - [Extensions/](mdc:ConfigForge/Extensions) - Swift extensions
  - [Styles/](mdc:ConfigForge/Styles) - UI style definitions
  - [Generated/](mdc:ConfigForge/Generated) - Generated code (SwiftGen)
  - [Assets.xcassets/](mdc:ConfigForge/Assets.xcassets) - App icons and image assets
  - [Resources/](mdc:ConfigForge/Resources) - Additional resources

